        <div class="mt-4 mb-4">
          <h2>Instructions</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Season the chicken breasts with salt and pepper.</li>
            <li>In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium-high heat.</li>
            <li>
              Add the chicken breasts and cook until golden brown and cooked
              through.
            </li>
            <li>Remove the chicken from the skillet and set aside.</li>
